[l] Kennt ihr den schon?Israel, Iran, Jordanien, Tuerkei und Zypern bauen einen Teilchenbeschleuniger in Jordanien?Nein, wirklich! Zwei-drei kleinere Set-Backs gab es auf dem Weg.For a start, Israel and Iran do not have diplomatic relations with each other and nor do fellow members Turkey and CyprusAt one point Iran was unable to pay its share because of international sanctions on bankingTwo Iranian scientists working on Sesame were killed in what the Iranian government said were assassinations by the Israeli secret serviceAfter a freak snowstorm, the Sesame roof collapsed leaving key components exposed to the elementsAber es ist doch fertig geworden und wird diese Tage eroeffnet. Das Forschungszentrum heisst Sesame, nach dem Ali Baba Maerchen.
